   *(Directly addresses the "does this work for my length?" question; one of the most common FAQs in the SERP)*

9. **The Finish That Makes or Breaks It: Topcoat, Gel, and the Plump Gloss Secret**
   *(Covers the "plump, cushiony" finish; BIAB/structured gel explanation; what to ask for at the salon vs DIY)*

10. **How to Make Rich Girl Nails Last — Maintenance and the 2-Week Rule**
    *(Longevity, gel vs regular wear, cuticle oil routine, touch-up tips; addresses the chip pain point)*

11. **Rich Girl Nail Inspo: 12 Looks to Screenshot for Your Next Appointment**
    *(Gallery-style inspiration section — sheer YNNB almond, micro-French, deep merlot, chocolate brown, soap nails, glazed almond; image-heavy — supports recommended image count)*

12. **From Rich Girl Nails to Your Full Aesthetic Universe**
    *(Closing contextual internal linking section — natural bridge to aesthetic-nail-ideas pillar and sub-cluster posts; editorial, not a link dump)*

